{"tid":207812,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"3DS 火紋跑已偷，日版限定開箱！","createTime":"2017-04-19T06:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T02:22:02.000Z","uid":84507,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f67aa494130917f23450af1c86b97cb893d1141f","tid":207812,"uid":84507,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:33:09.000Z","msg":"係香港真係幸福，人地要預訂既版本大家只要係各大game 鋪就可以買到。到底入面有啲咩呢？一齊來睇下！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aIbfD8uyjHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaIbfD8uyjHk&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QffiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9b219644\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aIbfD8uyjHk</a>"},{"pid":"3ec7a82ef6e11e56dc423dbfcacd9f0f011cf0a6","tid":207812,"uid":93190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:14:55.000Z","msg":"👍👍👍"},{"pid":"ba24ac990d02a0b3c6d5afcee190d92b45080e80","tid":207812,"uid":6366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:09:59.000Z","msg":"幸你老母福<br />\n人地訂左一定有你唔講<br />\n訂左正日一定有你唔講<br />\n幾缺貨都唔會炒你唔講<br />\n<br />\n垃圾game舖打手含撚啦"},{"pid":"b0d508805762a969c8a83f91303b107b07011cdb","tid":207812,"uid":84507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幸你老母福<br />\n人地訂左一定有你唔講<br />\n訂左正日一定有你唔講<br />\n幾缺貨都唔會炒你唔講<br />\n<br />\n垃圾game舖打手含撚啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你而家咪出街搵間GAME 鋪睇下邊度有炒貴到？<br />\n報個價來聽下？等大家搵貨都有心理準備嘛係咪？<br />\n我以為FORUM 係比人用來提供優質意見，你咩都唔講就話一定炒起左.....咁你講哂佢囉<br />\n訂左正日有....喂，聽講20號先正日喎，件野18號已經到香港<br />\n如果係真FANS，早兩日有，就算貴左都抵啦(仲要冇貴到添)<br />\n訂左一定有，咪一樣係有QUOTA，訂唔到咪一樣冇，到時搶到訂果D 咪一樣攞出來炒，只要炒得起，話知你香港定日本，一定有人炒，邊有人會嫌錢腥，睇比邊個賺啫！<br />\n<br />\n而且我成條片冇講過係邊度買，仲要講哂提防GAME 鋪換左你隻GAME 既手法出來.......黃金果堆仆街鋪頭睇到直頭想REPORT 我添啦<br />\n<br />\n如果大家咁都覺得係打手既，咪來回個覆評下理囉，咩先為之打手？"},{"pid":"30b2a609a961abbfabc9b61d2e950abd0e220a9e","tid":207812,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"一早唔係香港買game好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港市場個朵比班炒家搞臭晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b149f9e2a5a9da93ff1af21afcf71af70aee76","tid":207812,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"真fans就貴左都抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係外國真fans一早訂左唔撚駛煩啦<br />\n歐洲日本預訂平過正價咪一樣照有偷跑<br />\n<br />\n唔駛擔心坐地起價 唔駛擔心運上大陸都唔比貨你仲要hold你訂錢<br />\n一係就話唔要咪退訂囉<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係鬧你開箱分享<br />\n咁岩呢隻火紋 仲要外傳 香港人氣唔夠炒唔起<br />\n你就係到講咩香港買game好幸福<br />\n係Gamer 都知香港啲閪舖出名當客撚狗咁撚啦<br />\n前幾日先有個套餐 要買埋電視switch先有貨比你<br />\n你不如講下有咩地方有行貨都可以咁幸福啦"},{"pid":"68cc0e317051ce8cd1488776a537353b5ed917f7","tid":207812,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"香港game鋪食屎吧啦<br />\n<br />\n香港地火紋無人玩炒唔起當人地良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a73c9b5db1f8901e0a2a1309878cd80a73668d","tid":207812,"uid":57407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"係咪上集IF炒燶咗 今集先唔炒咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff5e8f933fcdec88bbd2744fec9117ab1f27f66","tid":207812,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"On撚9<br />\n連本設定集都要30皮<br />\n你同我講幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf9d7442708e9f2adb6e6dfb59910146e234917","tid":207812,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心定假膠"},{"pid":"3b3122299a179b1fb0b3a791702ab9df021182a1","tid":207812,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On撚9<br />\n連本設定集都要30皮<br />\n